---

<BaseLayout
  title="10-Day Tanzania Safari | Go Kilimanjaro Treks"
  description="Ten-day in-depth Tanzania safari across the Serengeti, Ngorongoro and supporting parks."
  schemas={schemas}
>
<section class="page-hero">
  <div class="container">
    <span class="page-hero-eyebrow">Tanzania Safari Itinerary</span>
    <h1>10-Day Tanzania Safari.</h1>
    <p>Ten-day in-depth Tanzania safari across the Serengeti, Ngorongoro and supporting parks.</p>
    <div class="hero-ctas">
      <a href="/contact" class="btn-primary">Request a Quote &#x2192;</a>
      <a href="https://wa.me/255677917500" class="btn-ghost" target="_blank" rel="noopener">&#x1F4AC; WhatsApp Nelson</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section-white">
  <div class="container" style="max-width:820px">
    <h2 style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-size:1.5rem;font-weight:700;color:var(--amber-cta);margin:32px 0 12px">10 Days Tanzania Safari &amp; Zanzibar Escape</h2>
    <p style="font-size:1rem;color:var(--text);line-height:1.78;margin-bottom:14px">Bush to Beach Experience - Wildlife, Culture &amp; Ocean Adventure</p>
    <p style="font-size:1rem;color:var(--text);line-height:1.78;margin-bottom:14px">Starting From USD 3,850 Per Person*</p>
    <p style="font-size:1rem;color:var(--text);line-height:1.78;margin-bottom:14px">Rates vary depending on season, accommodation type, and group size.</p>
    <h2 style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-size:1.5rem;font-weight:700;color:var(--amber-cta);margin:32px 0 12px">Safari Overview</h2>
    <p style="font-size:1rem;color:var(--text);line-height:1.78;margin-bottom:14px">This 10-day journey combines Tanzania's most iconic northern safari circuit with the tropical paradise of Zanzibar. The experience begins with classic game viewing in Tarangire, Ngorongoro, and Serengeti before transitioning into white sand beaches, turquoise waters, and marine adventures in the Indian Ocean.</p>
    <p style="font-size:1rem;color:var(--text);line-height:1.78;margin-bottom:14px">It is a balanced itinerary designed for wildlife lovers, honeymooners, photographers, and luxury travelers seeking both adventure and relaxation.</p>
    <h2 style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-size:1.5rem;font-weight:700;color:var(--amber-cta);margin:32px 0 12px">Day 1: Tarangire National Park - Land of Giants</h2>
    <p style="font-size:1rem;color:var(--text);line-height:1.78;margin-bottom:14px">Your safari begins after breakfast as you depart for Tarangire National Park, a wilderness famous for its massive elephant herds and ancient baobab trees.</p>
    <p style="font-size:1rem;color:var(--text);line-height:1.78;margin-bottom:14px">Enjoy a full-day game drive across golden savannahs where wildlife gathers around the Tarangire River. Expect elephants, lions, giraffes, zebras, buffaloes, and rich birdlife in a peaceful, less crowded ecosystem.</p>
    <p style="font-size:1rem;color:var(--text);line-height:1.78;margin-bottom:14px">Accommodation: Manyara Best View</p>
    <p style="font-size:1rem;color:var(--text);line-height:1.78;margin-bottom:14px">Board Basis: Full Board</p>
    <h2 style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-size:1.5rem;font-weight:700;color:var(--amber-cta);margin:32px 0 12px">Day 2: Ngorongoro Crater - The Natural Wonder</h2>
    <p style="font-size:1rem;color:var(--text);line-height:1.78;margin-bottom:14px">After breakfast, travel towards the Ngorongoro Conservation Area and descend into the spectacular Ngorongoro Crater.</p>
    <p style="font-size:1rem;color:var(--text);line-height:1.78;margin-bottom:14px">This UNESCO World Heritage Site offers one of the highest wildlife densities in Africa, including lions, elephants, buffaloes, hippos, hyenas, and the rare black rhino. The crater floor creates a natural amphitheatre of life surrounded by dramatic volcanic walls.</p>
    <p style="font-size:1rem;color:var(--text);line-height:1.78;margin-bottom:14px">Enjoy a picnic lunch inside the crater before ascending in the afternoon.</p>
    <p style="font-size:1rem;color:var(--text);line-height:1.78;margin-bottom:14px">Accommodation: Bougainvillea Lodge</p>
    <p style="font-size:1rem;color:var(--text);line-height:1.78;margin-bottom:14px">Board Basis: Full Board</p>
    <h2 style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-size:1.5rem;font-weight:700;color:var(--amber-cta);margin:32px 0 12px">Day 3: Serengeti National Park - Endless Plains Journey</h2>
    <p style="font-size:1rem;color:var(--text);line-height:1.78;margin-bottom:14px">Depart for Serengeti National Park through the scenic highlands and open landscapes of northern Tanzania.</p>
    <p style="font-size:1rem;color:var(--text);line-height:1.78;margin-bottom:14px">Upon arrival, begin your first game drive across vast savannahs filled with wildlife. The Serengeti is home to predators such as lions, cheetahs, and leopards, alongside large herds of herbivores roaming freely across the plains.</p>
    <p style="font-size:1rem;color:var(--text);line-height:1.78;margin-bottom:14px">Accommodation: Nyota Luxury Camp</p>
    <p style="font-size:1rem;color:var(--text);line-height:1.78;margin-bottom:14px">Board Basis: Full Board</p>
    <h2 style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-size:1.5rem;font-weight:700;color:var(--amber-cta);margin:32px 0 12px">Day 4: Serengeti Exploration - Wildlife Kingdom</h2>
    <p style="font-size:1rem;color:var(--text);line-height:1.78;margin-bottom:14px">Spend a full day exploring the heart of Serengeti National Park. Early morning and afternoon game drives provide excellent opportunities to observe predator activity and herd movements across the plains.</p>
    <p style="font-size:1rem;color:var(--text);line-height:1.78;margin-bottom:14px">Depending on the season, you may witness parts of the Great Migration, one of the most extraordinary wildlife events on Earth.</p>
    <p style="font-size:1rem;color:var(--text);line-height:1.78;margin-bottom:14px">A picnic lunch in the wilderness completes the experience.</p>
    <p style="font-size:1rem;color:var(--text);line-height:1.78;margin-bottom:14px">Accommodation: Enkutoto Migration Camp</p>
    <p style="font-size:1rem;color:var(--text);line-height:1.78;margin-bottom:14px">Board Basis: Full Board</p>
    <h2 style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-size:1.5rem;font-weight:700;color:var(--amber-cta);margin:32px 0 12px">Day 5: Flight to Zanzibar - Island Arrival &amp; Relaxation</h2>
    <p style="font-size:1rem;color:var(--text);line-height:1.78;margin-bottom:14px">After breakfast, transfer to the airstrip for your flight to Zanzibar Island. Upon arrival, you will be welcomed and driven to your beach resort.</p>
    <p style="font-size:1rem;color:var(--text);line-height:1.78;margin-bottom:14px">The rest of the day is free for relaxation-soft white sand, warm ocean breeze, and calm turquoise waters mark the beginning of your island escape.</p>
    <p style="font-size:1rem;color:var(--text);line-height:1.78;margin-bottom:14px">Accommodation: Zanzibar Beach Resort</p>
    <p style="font-size:1rem;color:var(--text);line-height:1.78;margin-bottom:14px">Board Basis: Half Board</p>
    <h2 style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-size:1.5rem;font-weight:700;color:var(--amber-cta);margin:32px 0 12px">Day 6: Prison Island - Turtle Encounter &amp; History Tour</h2>
    <p style="font-size:1rem;color:var(--text);line-height:1.78;margin-bottom:14px">Enjoy a boat excursion to Prison Island, home to giant tortoises and historical ruins.</p>
    <p style="font-size:1rem;color:var(--text);line-height:1.78;margin-bottom:14px">Explore the island, learn its history, and enjoy swimming in crystal-clear waters. The experience combines culture, nature, and relaxation in a single ocean adventure.</p>
    <p style="font-size:1rem;color:var(--text);line-height:1.78;margin-bottom:14px">Return to your resort in the afternoon for leisure time.</p>
    <p style="font-size:1rem;color:var(--text);line-height:1.78;margin-bottom:14px">Accommodation: Zanzibar Beach Resort</p>
    <p style="font-size:1rem;color:var(--text);line-height:1.78;margin-bottom:14px">Board Basis: Half Board</p>
    <h2 style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-size:1.5rem;font-weight:700;color:var(--amber-cta);margin:32px 0 12px">Day 7: Salaam Cave &amp; Stone Town Tour - Culture &amp; Heritage</h2>
    <p style="font-size:1rem;color:var(--text);line-height:1.78;margin-bottom:14px">Begin the day with a visit to Salaam Cave for a unique coastal and nature experience.</p>
    <p style="font-size:1rem;color:var(--text);line-height:1.78;margin-bottom:14px">Later, continue to Stone Town, a UNESCO World Heritage Site filled with narrow streets, carved doors, spice markets, and centuries of cultural influence from Africa, Arabia, and Europe.</p>
    <p style="font-size:1rem;color:var(--text);line-height:1.78;margin-bottom:14px">Enjoy a guided walking tour before returning to your resort.</p>
    <p style="font-size:1rem;color:var(--text);line-height:1.78;margin-bottom:14px">Accommodation: Zanzibar Beach Resort</p>
    <p style="font-size:1rem;color:var(--text);line-height:1.78;margin-bottom:14px">Board Basis: Half Board</p>
    <h2 style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-size:1.5rem;font-weight:700;color:var(--amber-cta);margin:32px 0 12px">Day 8: Safari Blue - Ocean Adventure Day</h2>
    <p style="font-size:1rem;color:var(--text);line-height:1.78;margin-bottom:14px">Today is dedicated to the famous Safari Blue experience. Sail on a traditional dhow across turquoise waters, snorkel in coral reefs, relax on sandbanks, and enjoy fresh seafood served on the beach.</p>
    <p style="font-size:1rem;color:var(--text);line-height:1.78;margin-bottom:14px">This is one of Zanzibar's most iconic marine experiences, combining adventure and relaxation.</p>
    <p style="font-size:1rem;color:var(--text);line-height:1.78;margin-bottom:14px">Accommodation: Zanzibar Beach Resort</p>
    <p style="font-size:1rem;color:var(--text);line-height:1.78;margin-bottom:14px">Board Basis: Half Board</p>
    <h2 style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-size:1.5rem;font-weight:700;color:var(--amber-cta);margin:32px 0 12px">Day 9: Nungwi - Jet Ski &amp; Beach Fun</h2>
    <p style="font-size:1rem;color:var(--text);line-height:1.78;margin-bottom:14px">Head to Nungwi Beach, one of Zanzibar's most vibrant coastal areas.</p>
    <p style="font-size:1rem;color:var(--text);line-height:1.78;margin-bottom:14px">Enjoy thrilling jet ski rides on the Indian Ocean, swim in clear waters, and relax on the white sandy beach. The area is perfect for both adventure and sunset relaxation.</p>
    <p style="font-size:1rem;color:var(--text);line-height:1.78;margin-bottom:14px">Return to your resort in the evening.</p>
    <p style="font-size:1rem;color:var(--text);line-height:1.78;margin-bottom:14px">Accommodation: Zanzibar Beach Resort</p>
    <p style="font-size:1rem;color:var(--text);line-height:1.78;margin-bottom:14px">Board Basis: Half Board</p>
    <h2 style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-size:1.5rem;font-weight:700;color:var(--amber-cta);margin:32px 0 12px">Day 10: Departure - Goodbye Tanzania</h2>
    <p style="font-size:1rem;color:var(--text);line-height:1.78;margin-bottom:14px">Enjoy a relaxed breakfast at your resort before transfer to Zanzibar Airport for your international departure.</p>
    <p style="font-size:1rem;color:var(--text);line-height:1.78;margin-bottom:14px">You leave with unforgettable memories of wildlife safaris, dramatic landscapes, and tropical ocean experiences.</p>
    <p style="font-size:1rem;color:var(--text);line-height:1.78;margin-bottom:14px">Board Basis: Half Board</p>
  </div>
</section>

